<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ACARA - Activate Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: lightgrey;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 5px auto;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -15px black;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ff3b3b;
        color: lightgrey;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: start;
      }
      .content ul {
        text-align: start;
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .content .group-verify {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content a.button-verif {
        font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
        font-size: 14px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        background-color: green;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 7px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .content p.valid-time {
        color: red;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin: 20px 25px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: darkslateblue;
        color: lightgrey;
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      @media (max-width: 500px) {
        .container {
          max-width: 100%;
          margin: 0;
          border-radius: 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header"><h1>Wellcome!</h1></div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
        <p>
          We appreciate you joining our service. Here is your account
          information:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span style="font-weight: bolder">Name :</span
            ><span> <%= fullName %></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span style="font-weight: bolder">Email :</span
            ><span> <%= email %></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span style="font-weight: bolder">Registration Date :</span
            ><span> <%= createdAt %></span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To verify your email address and activate your account, please click
          the button below:
        </p>
        <div class="group-verify">
          <a href="<%= verifyUrl %>" class="button-verif">Activate Account</a>
          <p class="valid-time">
            This link is valid for <%= expiresIn %> minutes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
        <p>Best regards, ACARA</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 ACARA Event Management App. All Right Reserved</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
